snippet.title: Killzone 2 e3 2005 trailer HD [BEST QUALITY ON YOUTUBE!]
snippet.description: I've personally been looking for an HD version of this trailer for a long time. I came across the best version I could find on Youtube. However, since that version has all kinds of cuts and a voiceover track, I spliced a few versions together to create this one (mainly the Kilzone 2 Blog version). It's still a little rough; you are free to try and fix it yourself if you want. I just wanted it to be out there in a viewable format.
